## ğŸ§  Agent Maturity Roadmap: From Level 0 to Level 5

| Level | Agent Capability | Strategic Focus | Key Gaps to Address |
|-------|------------------|------------------|---------------------|
| **Level 0** | **Prompt-only agents** | Static LLM wrappers with hardcoded prompts | No memory, no tools, no orchestration |
| **Level 1** | **Tool-augmented agents** | Basic function calling (e.g., search, calculator) | No planning, no control flow, brittle logic |
| **Level 2** | **Orchestrated agents** | Task decomposition, tool routing, retries | No memory, no governance, no modularity |
| **Level 3** | **Memory-enabled agents** | Working + long-term memory, context-aware | No personalization, no audit, no lifecycle |
| **Level 4** | **Multi-agent systems** | Planner + executor agents, collaboration | No control plane, no cost/compliance guardrails |
| **Level 5** | **Self-evolving agents** | Reflection, learning, adaptation, optimization | No feedback loops, no CI/CD, no policy engine |

---

## ğŸ§© Curated Steps to Progress Through Each Level

### ğŸ”¹ Level 0 â†’ Level 1: Tool-Augmented Agents
- âœ… Define callable tools (OpenAPI, LangChain schema)
- âœ… Build tool registry with metadata (latency, cost, domain)
- âœ… Enable basic function calling via LLM orchestration
- ğŸ”§ Missing: sandboxing, error handling, fallback logic

---

### ğŸ”¹ Level 1 â†’ Level 2: Orchestrated Agents
- âœ… Introduce orchestration layer (LangChain, Semantic Kernel, custom)
- âœ… Implement control flow: retries, branching, conditional logic
- âœ… Modularize agent logic into reusable components
- ğŸ”§ Missing: agent registry, lifecycle management, versioning

---

### ğŸ”¹ Level 2 â†’ Level 3: Memory-Enabled Agents
- âœ… Add working memory (session context, scratchpad)
- âœ… Add long-term memory (vector DB + structured store)
- âœ… Enable memory retrieval and update logic
- ğŸ”§ Missing: memory governance, user-specific context, ABAC policies

---

### ğŸ”¹ Level 3 â†’ Level 4: Multi-Agent Systems
- âœ… Define agent roles (planner, executor, verifier, retriever)
- âœ… Enable inter-agent communication and task handoff
- âœ… Introduce agent registry and ownership model
- ğŸ”§ Missing: unified control plane, IAM, audit trail, cost guardrails

---

### ğŸ”¹ Level 4 â†’ Level 5: Self-Evolving Agents
- âœ… Add reflection loop (evaluate, revise, retry)
- âœ… Integrate feedback signals (user ratings, success metrics)
- âœ… Enable agent tuning via CI/CD (prompt updates, tool swaps)
- âœ… Launch AgentOps dashboard (success rate, hallucination, cost)
- ğŸ”§ Missing: policy engine, rollback, canary testing, compliance hooks

