## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Cross-Cutting Enablers (Must Be Curated Throughout)

| Enabler | Description | Owner |
|---------|-------------|-------|
| **Unified Control Plane** | Agent registry, deployment, monitoring | AI Platform |
| **IAM & Policy Engine** | RBAC/ABAC, tool/data access, audit | Security & Compliance |
| **AgentOps** | Observability, debugging, performance tracking | AI Ops |
| **CI/CD for Agents** | GitOps-style deployment, rollback, versioning | DevOps |
| **LOB Templates** | Domain-specific agent blueprints | AI Strategy |

---

## ğŸš€ Final Outcome: Self-Evolving Agents

These agents will:
- Learn from feedback and revise their strategies
- Adapt tool usage and memory based on context
- Collaborate across roles and domains
- Operate within governed, compliant, and cost-aware boundaries

